1. create a instance with basic config
    add iam role with admin permissions
    
2. install terraform
    terraform.sh

3. create main.tf, variable.tf and .tfvars
    When we have multiple configurations for terraform to create resource
    like: dev,test,uat,prod.

4. terraform init		: initialize the provider plugins on backend

5. terraform apply		: to create resources
    terraform apply -var-file="dev.tfvars"

6. terraform destroy	: to delete resources
    terraform destroy -var-file="dev.tfvars"

